:{{DIcon|Talk}} About Capote...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500209404-->
::'''Lamina:''' He's actually been to see me, and his attitude was... a bit weird. I'm not saying he did anything funny, just... for someone who's usually so high and mighty to suddenly act so low feels really weird.
::'''Lamina:''' I couldn't even say anything when he stated how deeply he had reflected on himself and how sorry he was.
::'''Lamina:''' I don't know if I've totally put that time behind me and didn't care about what he could have said, or I never thought he'd apologize and was surprised he actually did it.
::'''Lamina:''' Anyways, I couldn't say anything to him and gave him zero responses.
::'''Lamina:''' But now that I think about it, he did show a look that I had never seen on his face before. Maybe that's... a "sincere" look? I hope he can keep being so sincere in the future.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What are your plans for the future?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500209410-->
::'''Lamina:''' Well... I've been doing mundane work all this time, but I somehow got to know lots of people in different departments.
::'''Lamina:''' Maybe a bit of good luck actually came from this. Lots of the previous Capote Fan Club members are senior researchers with independent projects under their care.
::'''Lamina:''' We knew each other because of our frequent interactions before. They got me to apply for some internal positions, and I managed to pass the interviews for a few projects. I'll probably be a "researcher" by the next time we meet.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} You are a very brave person.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500209414-->
::'''Lamina:''' I don't know about being brave...
::'''Lamina:''' If I really am brave, shouldn't I have said no to him the first time he oppressed me? Or should I have talked with him earlier, so that things wouldn't have to go down this way?
::'''Lamina:''' But instead of blaming myself for not having done enough, it's better to just admit that I've changed. I chose to face myself in this way and closed that chapter of my past.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all for now.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500209419-->
::'''Lamina:''' I'm going to start preparing for the preliminary work of the research project now. Hope we get the chance to chat again in the future.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Lamina:''' Hey, we meet again. What can I help you with?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Lamina:''' Anyways, thank you for saying these things to me.
:'''Lamina:''' I'm going to start preparing for the preliminary work of the research project now. Hope we get the chance to chat again in the future.
